name: Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac
short_description: Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac is an excellent iOS cleaner tool run on Mac OS X. It can scan and strike out almost any kind of junk files on iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch to release the clumsy storage space. Whenever you found your iPhone running slow or running out of space, you can ask help from iPhone Cleaner for Mac. It give a effective solution to clean up your device and reclaim the lost space to speed up your iPhone and get more apps, music, movies, photos and fun in your life. Macgo iPhone Cleaner for Mac run on Mac OS X 10.8 or above and is compatible with iPhone, iPad, iPod touch(iOS 5, 6, 7). Note: Please note you must install the latest iTunes to enable cleaner to work. What's new in version 1.0.3? 1-Fully compatible with iOS 8 and perfectly support OS X Yosemite Beta 10.10. 2-Solve the problem of collapse when users shut down the program. 3-The information of the devices can now be successfully saved in the program.
